{"tid":2352664,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"讀者爆料《全民造星》Manson拍拖靠黐 被飛編劇女友貼錢長租觀塘酒店做私竇","createTime":"2021-01-04T07:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T23:08:59.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"f7bb09ba90c710fa0883a3279faff1c6905ea6ab","tid":2352664,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:29:09.000Z","msg":"23 歲Manson張進翹，去年參加《全民造星III》後，一直人氣高企。人紅自然是非多，最近有報導指Manson在參賽初期，跟ViuTV劇集《娛樂風雲》的編劇李欣如（Lily）撻著。由於節目播出後，Manson因貌似Beyond 主音黃家駒，火速成為焦點 。有傳他為了保住偶像光環，即刻同女友斬䌫。事後Manson透過經理人公司承認，跟Lily 拍拖一個月，因性格不合而分手，絕對同入行無關。<br />\n<br />\n不過，最近本刊收到讀者報料，指二人拍拖期間，一切食、住、行等使費，都由女友負責。為方便見面，Lily更出錢在觀塘長租酒店房做私竇。但Lily依然維護前男友，並表示：「我哋一直都係朋友&hellip;&hellip;.！」<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_772143_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_772143_0&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyeSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=db390b4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_772143_0&h=4441030c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_772143_0</a>"},{"pid":"cf305820fdf947001bc8d04724cbd3628af8231c","tid":2352664,"uid":137569,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:31:22.000Z","msg":"邊忽似家駒<br />\n髮型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab197d9a433524a64e119af3fb4af7922143ec64","tid":2352664,"uid":157128,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:34:55.000Z","msg":"第一句就錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nManson 27歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820ddb53038645852441da6faac4895fdeadb2be","tid":2352664,"uid":21470,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:37:45.000Z","msg":"蘋果娛記既mean筆唔做港聞真係曬晒"},{"pid":"fc678f2775b00c34a68a101cc17a68d309143df4","tid":2352664,"uid":16775,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":4